        <Parent_String>Venetian glass [300136735], glass by technique [300010831], glass (material) [300010797], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
